    public class MyHabitHistory
extends android.support.v7.app.AppCompatActivity
implements FilterDialog.FilterDialogListener
    This activity allows the user to view their own habit history of all habits they have created, sorted by date. The user may choose to filter the habit events by habit type and/or comment. OUSTANDING ISSUES: Because the filter uses regex, searching for special characters causes a crash
